            <title><![CDATA[【周知！#热射病急救关键是补水降温#[话筒]】#热射病与中暑有何区别#？医生介绍，热射病是中暑的最严重类型，死亡率极高。临床诊断有3个特点：①高温环境暴露；...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【周知！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%83%AD%E5%B0%84%E7%97%85%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E6%98%AF%E8%A1%A5%E6%B0%B4%E9%99%8D%E6%B8%A9%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%83%AD%E5%B0%84%E7%97%85%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E5%85%B3%E9%94%AE%E6%98%AF%E8%A1%A5%E6%B0%B4%E9%99%8D%E6%B8%A9%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#热射病急救关键是补水降温#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%83%AD%E5%B0%84%E7%97%85%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%AD%E6%9A%91%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%83%AD%E5%B0%84%E7%97%85%E4%B8%8E%E4%B8%AD%E6%9A%91%E6%9C%89%E4%BD%95%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#热射病与中暑有何区别#</span></a>？医生介绍，热射病是中暑的最严重类型，死亡率极高。临床诊断有3个特点：①高温环境暴露；②核心体温超过40℃；③中枢神经系统功能改变，同时还有一些脏器功能受损。出现热射病相关症状要及时降温补水，可以用冷水浸泡全身、用冰袋进行冰敷、用温水洒满全身。如何预防热射病？👇🏻<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4920994901459010" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hfopl4vad5j60uo14w7wh02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/ZuQpORDzlx086PrwJFxC01041200OpVR0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1Cw5miNEOurLOz&amp;Expires=1688822743&amp;ssig=Vx57vYMKjZ&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/OWVCRerxlx086PryteQM01041200tpbu0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1Cw5miNEOurLOz&amp;Expires=1688822743&amp;ssig=qfniiW1Bjl&amp;KID=un